      <h1 style="color: #032B22; font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif !important">Welcome to Our Dog Walking Guide!</h1>
      <p class="font-dog-walk-guide" class="font-dog-walk-guide">Your go-to resource for everything dog walking—tailored tips, expert advice, and insights to keep your pup happy, healthy, and active!</p>
